data.description: Welcome to a spacious 3-bedroom home that exudes modern comfort and style. With 4 bathrooms, a 2-car garage, and a walk-out basement, this property offers abundant space and functionality. Fresh landscaping and newer paint create an inviting curb appeal, setting the stage for the beauty within. Step inside to discover granite countertops, hardwood floors, and a wood-burning fireplace that adds warmth and character. The radon mitigation system ensures safety and peace of mind. A large deck and yard beckon you to enjoy the outdoors, while the master suite with a tub and separate shower pampers you with luxury. Freshly painted kitchen cabinets and a finished basement complete this attractive package, making it the perfect place to call home.
